              "latency_ms": 4454.757374944165,
              "response": "Token budget allocation when using shared context collections is structured based on the importance of document categories. The allocation is as follows:\n\n- **Project-specific documents** receive 40% of the total budget.\n- **MANDATORY** documents receive 25% of the total budget.\n- **BEST_PRACTICES** documents receive 20% of the total budget.\n- **GUIDELINES** documents receive 10% of the total budget.\n- **REFERENCE** documents receive 5% of the total budget.\n\nThis means that when querying, the system prioritizes project-specific documents first, followed by shared documents categorized by their importance (MANDATORY, BEST_PRACTICES, GUIDELINES, REFERENCE) (5.1 Budget Allocation Logic).",
